Package: poppler1
Version: 0.5.1
Revision: 21
Description: PDF rendering library
License: GPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <poppler1@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: %N-shlibs (= %v-%r)
BuildDepends: cairo (>= 1.0.0-1), expat, fontconfig2-dev, freetype219, glib2-dev (>= 2.8.6-122), gettext-bin, gettext-tools, gtk+2-dev, gettext-dev, libiconv-dev, libjpeg, pango1-xft2-dev, pkgconfig, x11-dev
Conflicts: poppler
Replaces: poppler
BuildDependsOnly: True
GCC: 3.3

Source: http://poppler.freedesktop.org/poppler-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: a136cd731892f4570933034ba97c8704
PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/%n.patch | patch -p1

SetLIBS: -L%p/lib -lexpat
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man SYSTEM_XPDFRC=%p/etc/xpdfrc.poppler1 --disable-dependency-tracking --enable-zlib --disable-poppler-qt --disable-poppler-qt4 FREETYPE_CONFIG=%p/lib/freetype219/bin/freetype-config PKG_CONFIG_PATH=%p/lib/fontconfig2/lib/pkgconfig

InstallScript: <<
  perl -pi -e 's,Requires:,Requires: cairo >= 1.0.0,' poppler-glib.pc
  make install DESTDIR=%d
  install -d %i/etc
  install -c -m 644 xpdfrc.poppler1 %i/etc/
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog NEWS README README-XPDF TODO
SplitOff: <<
	Package: %N-shlibs
	Depends: cairo-shlibs (>= 1.0.0-1), expat-shlibs, fontconfig2-shlibs, freetype219-shlibs, glib2-shlibs (>= 2.8.6-122), gtk+2-shlibs, gettext, libiconv, libjpeg-shlibs, pango1-xft2-shlibs, x11-shlibs
	Replaces: poppler (<< %v-%r), %N (<< %v-%r)
	DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog NEWS README README-XPDF TODO
	Files: <<
		lib/libpoppler.*.dylib
		lib/libpoppler-glib.*.dylib
		etc
	<<
	Shlibs: <<
		%p/lib/poppler.1.dylib 2.0.0 poppler1--shlibs (>= 0.5.1-1)
		%p/lib/poppler-glib.1.dylib 2.0.0 poppler1-shlibs (>= 0.5.1-1)
	<<
	ConfFiles: %p/etc/xpdfrc.poppler1
<<
SplitOff2: <<
	Package: poppler-bin
	Depends: %N-shlibs (>= %v-%r)
	Conflicts: xpdf
	Replaces: poppler (<< %v-%r), %N (<< %v-%r), xpdf
	DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog NEWS README README-XPDF TODO
	Files: bin share/man
<<

Homepage: http://poppler.freedesktop.org/
DescDetail: Poppler is a PDF rendering library based on the xpdf-3.0 code base.
DescPackaging:   fontconfig2 is static-only on 10.3, shared on 10.4* distros.
DescPort: <<
xpdfrc file borrowed from xpdf. It is renamed xpdfrc.poppler to avoid
a conflict with xpdf.  Cairo output is disabled because it makes poppler
crash.

Patched Makefile.in to get freetype linker flags. See:
https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=4154
<<

